  "title": "Principal Consultant",
  "description": "<ul><li>Must have 8+ years of experience in delivering Data, Analytics, BI, and ETL/Informatica projects preferably in banking environment.</li><li>Strong expertise in end-to-end project delivery, governance, change control, and compliance with SDM/audit requirements.</li><li>Proven experience in managing Agile/Scrum delivery, sprint ceremonies, UAT coordination, and stakeholder reporting across onshore/offshore teams.</li><li>Hands-on experience in Informatica PowerCenter, SQL, data warehousing, ETL optimization, and BI tools (like Qlik, Power BI, Tableau).</li><li>Skilled in vendor management, regulatory/risk coordination, and deployment readiness across enterprise platforms (Jira, Confluence, ServiceNow).</li><li>Demonstrated ability to drive operational efficiency through automation, workflow optimization, and data-driven reporting solutions.</li></ul>",
